  "title": "Savory Showy Portuguese Puy Lentils Skillet",
  "description": "A hearty lacto-vegetarian Portuguese dish featuring nutty puy lentils with a cheesy pull, made in a wok with blanched and seasoned namul, perfect for a show-off dinner",
